fields.name: Chiedo Labs
fields.description: Technology can be incredible when implemented correctly, and we know how to implement. Chiedo Labs was founded in 2012 by Chiedo John during his last semester at James Madison University and has been growing rapidly ever since. We want to contribute to technology that has been set up the right way, with a focus on the web. If you are looking for a team of coders to support your team or project, we are definitely the team for the job. Currently we are based in the Shenandoah Valley of Virginia but have clients nationwide and overseas.
